    "updated_at": "2024-08-26T03:56:28Z",
    "body": "I see a lot of this same issue is caused by using `nix_shell` module which is using the `❄️` emoji by default. Maybe the easiest workaround is to use `󱄅` (\\udb84\\udd05) instead. It's supported by Nerd Font and it's displaying right in my terminal.",
